# Merkle-based ADS Experiment

Experiment Data for Merkle vector identifier tree:

```
go run mht_iden.go
```

Experiment Data for SP constructing merkle tree Time:

```
go run   float_6_4_to_byte.go
```
Experiment Data for VO read and verfiy Time:


```
go run   mytest_4_9.go
```


Firstly, we obtain the node IDs used in the HNSW search process during the [experiment](/experiment/hnsw), and then, based on these IDs, we generate the Verification Objects (VO) using the ADS. The node IDs look similar to the following:
